attributes.Long form description: The student turns the rolling cart and begins to unscrew each one of the wheels, then turns the rolling cart again and unscrews the hexagon cap nuts of the middle tray, continues with the top tray and unscrews it in the same way, when finished places the top tray on the table, at the same time disassembles the middle tray and places it on the other tray. Next, the student unscrews the bottom tray, detaches it from the base frame, and stacks it together with the other two trays. Then unscrews the two side bars and removes them. Finally,  disassembles the two base frames places them on the table, and stops recording.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the first wheel.
